[src:dynamical-systems-math/lyapunov-stability] The origin $N=0$ is an equilibrium point.
[src:dynamical-systems-math/lyapunov-stability] We aim to derive conditions that make $N=0$ a uniformly stable and an asymptotically stable extinction equilibrium.
